oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Andrews, Julia W., 1923 May 28
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Julia W. Andrews, dated April 21st, 1917. Illustrates the first page of the document. Andrews’ will was presented for probate to the Davidson County Court on May 28th, 1923. Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
